notes.title: Study Tips
notes.content:
1. Take regular breaks
2. Stay organized
3. Practice active recall

notes.title: HI LOVEEEEEEEEEEEEE
notes.content:
So, eto na HAHAHAHAHAH ito na yung study tool para sa iyo, hindi pa perfect talaga like hindi pa maka use ng pictures dito sa notes pero dont worry mag make na ako update para sa tool mo hehehehehe.

I know na very pagod ka and I hope na somehow maka help ito sa iyo pero sure ako hindi mo na toh gagamitin after 1 month HAHAHAHAHAHAHHA, anyways love, baby heheheheh nagpapansin lang ako through here HAHAHAHAHAHAHA. Sure ako pagsend ako ito sa iyo maya pa ma view mo and its fine as long as you are well rested my love. I dont even know if ma save ito pag send ko sa iyo ang folder. 

Baby just know I love you so much, I really do and I want to help you in any way shape or form kahit malayo ako, kahit aawayin mo ko para ma relieve stress mo. Basta nandito lang ako, I will be here kahit nasa screen lang ako, I will keep loving you all day, every day, all night, every night, all time every time. I love you babyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy mwaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa, ok dito muna ang I guess letter ko HAHAHHAHAHAHHA, pang motivation mo.
